I"Ù<p>Here are some examples of what a post with images might look like. If you want to display two or three images next to each other responsively use <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">figure</code> with the appropriate <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">class</code>. Each instance of <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">figure</code> is auto-numbered and displayed in the caption.</p>

